Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,RISE, KNIGHT OF DESTINY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Hey! What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dai! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?! You're Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me! Who are you?!\NWhat is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it capture Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't answer all that at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Goroa, the Drumbler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I oversee the heart of Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You fly Ban Palace from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is this monster?!\NWhy did it take Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's based on an organism,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's a Dark Force Reactor\Nthat's half machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. That controls Ban Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Force Reactor\Nis the heart that drives Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dark Force Reactor\Ndraws on my Magic Power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and transmits it\Nacross all of Ban Palace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a living engine. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks to that spell\Nthe girl cast, Minakator,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it has lost the ability\Nto draw on my Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Starved for Magic Power,\Nit's gone berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:04:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Dark Force Reactor extended\Nits tentacles to search for Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So it went after Leona\Nbecause of her high Magic Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... me and Popp are also here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! Master Aban's Feathers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With Master Aban gone, Leona currently\Nholds the greatest source of Magic Power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona! That thing is drawn\Nto the Magic Power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Feathers Master gave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to drop all the Feathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! I'll have to destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, King Ban will punish me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you stop that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to control\Nthe Dark Force Reactor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban gave me the power\Nto control super gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using it as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not stopping at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That shows how wildly\Nthe Dark Force Reactor's rampaging!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stop the Gravity Pulse\Nfrom my belly, it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl will be eaten\Nby the Dark Force Reactor and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, any creature caught by\Nthose tentacles would be absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you should be thanking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!\NIt's like an invisible wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He seems to be incredibly strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate, he'll destroy\Nthe Dark Force Reactor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that happens,\NKing Ban is sure to execute me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good! Nothing's working!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case,\Nthere's some risk to Leona...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll have to cut it in two\Nwith an Aban Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}Aban...!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I hit you with a Gravity Pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,\NI'm under no obligation to help that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can kill the Hero,\NI'll be rewarded for my achievement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my chance to get out of\Nlife in the bilge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! If he's directing\Nhis Gravity Pulse at me...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite powerful. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was tasked with holding\Nthat giant Dark Force Reactor in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power can't beat mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That said, how am I supposed to\Nfinish him of?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Get up! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry or Leona will be... Leona will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll only take a few more seconds\Nfor her to be absorbed and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I stab you with this sword,\Nnot even you can survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I defeat the Hero,\NKing Ban will commend me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do things if I set my mind to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To be killed by a little grunt like Goroa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,only moments before the final battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For a Hero,\Nthat's a rather pathetic ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over until it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it's over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still trying to resist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit still and die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darn it.. Dragon Crest...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this... Is this really...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all the strength that I have?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even while I'm using\Nall that I have within me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all a Dragon Knight can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Dragon Knights... really this weak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect someone I care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't I have the power to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tears of frustration.\NBut it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be smarter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now die by your own sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when Mom died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The life of a Dragon Knight\Nis one of unending battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught in that bloody path...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems many a woman\Nhas met a tragic ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, your mother was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever the past may be, you are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,By your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,see if you can end the sad fate\Nof the Dragon Knights, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when you first rescued Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are no normal Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry my soul.\NYou are a new Super Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand! Stand up! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first time the power of my Crest awoke\Nwas when I rescued Leona!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Draw it out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That unknown power within me!\NJust like back then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My power and that of Dad's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,are much more than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.48,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGA STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.49,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABRAKE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Crests... on each fist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The power in my left hand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is Dad's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will be with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the battle ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We shall always be together,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}never to part again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time,\Nthe power of Dad's Crest entered me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That why I saw Mom,\Neven though I've never met her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was Dad's soul reassuring me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inside me... all this time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad was always there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Baran's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Dragon Crests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They are... Twin Dragon Crests!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My Gravity Pulse isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Crest Beam!{\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Dark Force Reactor's barrier...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Twin Dragon Crests are a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the fortune telling of a Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The predictions always come true\Nin a bad way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Her clothes may be all torn up,\Nbut she's completely unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Goroa said that thing would absorb\Nyour body, so I was really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You took care of it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But my clothes are ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was first grabbed,\NI felt really weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Force Reactor really does absorb\Ncreatures for their Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, could you turn around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan shrunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan was inside my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside your clothes?! Where inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It doesn't matter where!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan must have protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be that while I was inside\Nthe Dark Force Reactor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan was emitting\NMagic Power the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what kept me from being absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what caused the shrinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But Gomechan's helped us\Nin numerous battles up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Gomechan have some mysterious power?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}healing Dai's stamina,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and allegedly calling Popp back\Nfrom the brink of death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And with Chiu,\Nattacking with a hardened body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for me, emitting Magic Power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what is Gomechan's true power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not question\Nsomeone who saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Gomechan\Nis kind of cute this small.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just let Gomechan rest for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I said don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to make sure\NI knew where Gomechan would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Goroa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've left me with no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pour all of my Magic Power\Ninto the Dark Force Reactor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and take you down with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any other option!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Dark Force Reactor is lost,\NI will not hold you responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems that the great wheels of fate\Nhave sided with the Hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he had climbed\Nthe Tower of Supremacy unchallenged,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai would have been no threat to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other Dark Force Reactors\Nin the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't provoke Dai any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be your order, King Ban...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't turn back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two Dragon Crests?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just some ordinary spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my Dad's...\NIt's the Dragon Knight's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,greatest and strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ace in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Doru Aura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Doru Aura fired from the Twin Dragon\NCrests obliterated the Dark Force Reactor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At last Dai and Leona reach the top\Nof the Tower of Supremacy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There awaits Dark King Ban\Nbrimming with deadly intent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's fears resurface\Nwith his rematch against Ban,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the Kōmanotsue closes in.{\i0}
